Subject: Re: [T2] Aftermarket S-Boots

I would think you could coat/cover the entire boot (cork/tape  the
connections) with a liquid rubber or silicone.  When the flapper box on
my heaterbox to heatube rusted through and was paperthin, I encased it
in a layer of epoxy.  The good epoxy easily takes 500 degrees.
